### Account Context

{%- if account_strategy == 'Multi-Account (Domain-based)' %}
**Domain-Based Strategy**
This account represents a business domain. In the next step, you'll confirm which domain this account belongs to.

**Object Naming:** Since the domain is at the account level, database names will NOT include the domain (avoiding redundancy). Example: `<dataproduct>_<zone>_<env>`

{%- elif account_strategy == 'Multi-Account (Environment-based)' %}
**Environment-Based Strategy**
This account represents an SDLC environment. In the next step, you'll confirm which environment this account belongs to.

**Object Naming:** Since the environment is at the account level, database names will NOT include the environment (avoiding redundancy). Example: `<domain>_<dataproduct>_<zone>`

{%- elif account_strategy == 'Multi-Account (Domain + Environment)' %}
**Domain + Environment Strategy**
This account represents a specific domain-environment combination. In the next step, you'll confirm both values.

**Object Naming:** Since both domain and environment are at the account level, database names will NOT include them (avoiding redundancy). Example: `<dataproduct>_<zone>`

{%- endif %}

